text:
:wave: Hello! I’ve been part of this community pretty much since the beginning, but I have recently made a switch, so I thought now would be a good time to reconnect with y’all :smile:

About a month ago I joined <http://toggl.com/track|Toggl Track> as their Marketing Director and went from focussing on SEO and content to leading (and growing — we’re currently hiring) a fully fledged marketing team. Both very exciting and a little challenging!

Apart from work, I enjoy running, reading, and spending time with my dogs. Happy to be part of this community and excited to connect with all of you!

attachments.title: Toggl Track: Time Tracking Software for Any Workflow
attachments.text: The world's best time tracking software. Track employee time, send beautiful client reports, and calculate profitability. Free and paid plans to save you time.

text: I starting using Toggl for the first time in November, and I’ve been really impressed. I’m sure it does more than what I use it for, but for basic time tracking, it required no training for me to use, the UI is refreshing, and I love the dashboards and reports! Well done to you and the Toggl team. :slightly_smiling_face:
